    "summary": "I am a Marketing professional with expertise in Strategic Market Management, Branding, Communication, Events and Campaigns, Alliance/ Partner Marketing and Project Management amongst others. I have a track record of working through challenging and ambiguous marketing ecosystem and changing organizational structure. In a world of rapidly shifting technologies, I strongly believe the objective of Marketing is not trying to sell, instead to help customers buy.\n\nCurrently I'm the Marketing Head of GTM initiatives for TCS Interactive and New Business Model Group. In this position my charter is to drive the brand recognition and customer demand for TCS\u2019 award wining digital services and products. Over the years i have managed and led various marketing functions across industry and regions, Enterprise Applications and consulting services, marketing for Midmarket segment, Market Analysis, Pipeline Management, Marketing Operations and Project Management during my stint with IBM Global Business Services, IBM Software Group and TCS Marketing and customer teams.\n\nMy interest is in converting the ever changing business priorities into Marketing actions with measurable outcome. I cherish the multi-cultural and diverse environment I work in and thrive to lead integration and effective team collaboration.\n\nI hold a Master in Business Management from Institute of Chartered Financial Analysts of India, and a Bachelor in Electronics and Communication Engineering. I am a professionally trained SAP SCM consultant from Siemens Academy and an amateur classical Guitarist!\n\nFurther I am passionate about issues related to digitalization and sustainable growth, clean energy, climate change and economic equity and contribute whenever there is an opportunity. \n\nYou can contact me via this profile or mail me at nirupam299@rediffmail.com",
